class Foo {}

// Suppress multiple rules for the annotated construct
@Suppress("ktlint:standard:no-wildcard-imports", "ktlint:custom-rule-set-id:custom-rule-id")
import foo.*

// Suppress all rules for the annotated construct
@Suppress("ktlint")
import foo.*
```

!!! warning "Deprecated directives"
    The `ktlint-disable` and `ktlint-enable` comment-based directives have been removed as of KtLint version `1.0`. Use `@Suppress` annotations instead.

    A new rule `no-deprecated-ktlint-directive` detects the usage of deprecated directives and reports them."}

